  <datafield tag="500" ind1=" " ind2=" ">
    <subfield code="a">Anne Cropper expresses sympathy for anti-slavery efforts and thanks Maria Weston Chapman for the volumes of the Liberty Bell. She is deeply interested in the question of the annexation of Texas and refers to the awful manner in which &quot;two of the warm abettors of that iniquitous measure&quot; were cut off by Providence.</subfield>
  </datafield>
